CREATE TABLE parquetfile
USING PARQUET
LOCATION "abfss://prasynapsefs0820@prasynapsesa0820.dfs.core.windows.net/CustomerCases/canzius"

%%pyspark
df = spark.sql("""
   SELECT Id, Identifier, Created, Updated, Expires, Anonymized, CommitRequested, CommitCompleted, CommitReference, CommitErrorCode, 
   CommitErrorDescription, Deleted, OrderId, Data, ExternalReference FROM parquetfile
""") 
display(df)
df.write.saveAsTable("canziusparquet")

%%spark
val df = spark.sql("SELECT * FROM canziusparquet")
df.write.sqlanalytics("prasynapsep0820.dbo.canziusparquet", Constants.INTERNAL )
